   EXPIRATION 8
   LINES 65
   COLUMNS 80
   PRINTFORMAT X_PAPER
   BANNER D
   RECIPIENT GRIMMETTDAVI
   PRINTDEPARTMENT BFIT-Akron
   ARCMODE PRINT
   IF ESPSHH = '12' THEN RUN WORKDAYS
   IF ESPSHH = '12' THEN EARLYSUB 16.00
   /* NORUN HOLIDAY
ENDJOB


